  <description><![CDATA[<p>The enchanting village of Balestrand is on a peninsula of orchards and farmland, on the northern shores of the famous Sognefjord - Norway's longest and deepest fjord that stretches over 200 kilometres. Balestrand’s backdrop of towering snow-capped mountains and panoramic vistas is mesmerising. The village is well connected, with buses and express boats operatig in all directions, so it's the bprfet base for exploring and the Flåm railway, Fjærland ferry and Jøstedal Glacier are just some of the main attractions to see when you're here. </p>
<p>There is also much opportunity to simply relax amidst the peaceful surroundings or enjoying the superb scenery from a bicycle or row boat. Balestrand also gives you access to spectacular walking territory with trails rising behind the village to the peaks and lakes of the plateau beyond.</p>
<p><strong>Multi-centres</strong></p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/115a7485cd0c44498faef1f70721b2b3" href="/{localLink:umb://document/115a7485cd0c44498faef1f70721b2b3}" title="Taste of Norway">Taste of Norway</a> is a twin centre combination where you can explore the city of <a data-udi="umb://document/d517b2c21fa94eb096a3bcb6b7e933c5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/d517b2c21fa94eb096a3bcb6b7e933c5}" title="Bergen">Bergen</a> before taking the express boat to Balestrand.</p>
<p>If you wanted to tick off a couple more resorts in <a data-udi="umb://document/286d71b6bae94f84a7ac63448c015f54" href="/{localLink:umb://document/286d71b6bae94f84a7ac63448c015f54}" title="Norway">Norway</a>, then the <a data-udi="umb://document/a9bd29bd99244343b8f3ab2d2faa7ca7" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a9bd29bd99244343b8f3ab2d2faa7ca7}" title="Fjord Explorer">Fjord Explorer</a> will be the perfect holiday. Start here before travelling through the fjords to <a data-udi="umb://document/14f6ab787ad2493ab23ce60aa9f14e6a" href="/{localLink:umb://document/14f6ab787ad2493ab23ce60aa9f14e6a}" title="Loen">Loen</a> and <a data-udi="umb://document/4796d8535a46439d92020f8a158e7c03" href="/{localLink:umb://document/4796d8535a46439d92020f8a158e7c03}" title="Alesund">Alesund</a>.</p>
<p>Both of our escorted tours, <a data-udi="umb://document/0dc506c20a05408bb514ab25ad4f8aad" href="/{localLink:umb://document/0dc506c20a05408bb514ab25ad4f8aad}" title="Highlights of the Fjords">Highlights of the Fjords</a> and <a data-udi="umb://document/a185e24ce7df443483a5ff2d8bb68c56" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a185e24ce7df443483a5ff2d8bb68c56}" title="Bergen to Oslo Fjord Experience">Bergen to Oslo Fjord Experience</a> have great time in Balestrand.</p>
<p> </p>]]></description>
