  <walkingDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Popular walks in and aroaund Balestrand include: </strong></p>
<p><strong>Easy: </strong>Balestrand has a few gentle half to full day trips from nearby Kreklingen, including the Heritage trail and the Nature trail, which are the easiest from the selection.</p>
<p><strong>Moderate:</strong> For bit more of a challenge try one of the blue trails, which are steeper and take you higher for better views.</p>
<p><strong>Slightly Challenging:</strong> Or for a day out, head to Dragsvik either by ferry or walk around the Esefjord (approx. 2hrs each way). From the lookout in Dragsvik, you have a view over 3 fjord branches.</p>]]></walkingDescription>
